[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_ik3xl")
reagent_id = "CO2"
title = "Carbon dyoxide"
body = "[b]Basic facts[/b]
[table=2]
[cell]Formula:[/cell][cell]CO₂[/cell]
[cell]Molar mass:[/cell][cell]44 g/mol[/cell]
[cell]State at room temperature:[/cell][cell]Gas[/cell]
[cell]Color:[/cell][cell]Colorless[/cell]
[cell]Smell:[/cell][cell]Odorless[/cell]
[cell]Density:[/cell][cell]Heavier than air[/cell]
[/table]
[b]Formation reaction[/b]
C + O₂ → CO₂  
C + SO₂ → CO₂ + S
[b]Important properties[/b]
• Does not support combustion.
• Dissolves in water to form carbonic acid (H₂CO₃).
• Produced during respiration and combustion.
[b]Where carbon dioxide is found[/b]
• In the atmosphere (~0.04%).
• Produced by living organisms during respiration.
• Released when fuels burn.
[b]Uses[/b]
• In carbonated drinks.
• In fire extinguishers.
• Used in greenhouses to help plants grow.
• Dry ice (solid CO₂) is used for cooling.
[b]Safety[/b]
Not toxic in small amounts, but high concentrations can cause suffocation."
